      high: `To continue growing, ${name} should work on fitting linear models to data, interpreting correlation coefficients, analyzing two-way frequency tables, and comparing data sets using formal statistical reasoning.`,
      mid: `To strengthen performance in this area, ${name} should practice constructing and interpreting box plots and scatter plots, calculating mean absolute deviation, applying probability rules to compound events, and drawing inferences from samples.`,
